Dim iRow,iCol Dim xmlDoc, xmlRoot Dim xmlNodes, xmlData
Dim oXML, oXSLNode Set oXML = CreateObject("MSXML2.DOMDocument") 'Set xmlData = CreateObject("MSXML2.IXMLDOMNode")' 'Set oXSLNode = CreateObject("MSXML2.IXMLDOMNode")' 'Set xmlData = CreateObject("MSXML2.IXMLDOMNode")'
Set objExcel = CreateObject("Excel.Application") objExcel.Visible = true Set objWorkbook = objExcel.Workbooks.Add() Set objWorksheet = objWorkbook.Worksheets(1)
oXML.async = False oXML.validateOnParse = False oXML.Load"${#TestCase#XMLfileLocation}"
Set xmlRoot = oXML.DocumentElement Set xmlNodes = xmlRoot.FirstChild
iRow = 0 For Each xmlNodes In xmlRoot.ChildNodes iRow = iRow + 1 iCol = 0
For Each xmlData In xmlNodes.ChildNodes iCol = iCol + 1 objWorksheet.Cells(1, iCol) = xmlData.BaseName objWorksheet.Cells(iRow, iCol) = xmlData.Text Next
Next
Wscript.Echo "conversion done"
objWorkbook.SaveAs "C:\Users\NikitaChhattani\Desktop\Furloughproject\Marvel\vbsTest.xlsx" Wscript.Echo "File Saved"
Wscript.Quit
